comment: Millsap (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as he follows Wiggins' (MIN) path to the basket and does not affect his RSBQ.
Dieng (MIN) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm while reaching in from behind and causes him to lose the ball.
LaVine (MIN) moves his pivot foot.
Burke (UTA) does not obtain legal guarding position and makes contact with LaVine's (MIN) body, which affects his shot attempt.
Brown's (MIN) contact on the perimeter does not affect Burke's (UTA) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
LaVine (MIN) commits a take foul on Millsap (UTA).
Brown (MIN) commits a take foul on Burke (UTA).
Dieng (MIN) initiates incidental contact with Favors (UTA) who then bumps into Brown (MIN) on the screen, but Brown is given enough room to stop and/or change direction.
Dieng (MIN) maintains legal guarding position as he hedges on the screen and does not affect Burke's (UTA) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Favors (UTA) undercuts Brown (MIN) as he catches the blocked shot and shoots all in the same motion.
Dieng (MIN) holds Gobert (UTA) and restricts his FOM on the perimeter.
Brown (MIN) affects Burke's (UTA) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Gobert (UTA) sticks his hip out into Brown (MIN) on the screen and does not give him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Brown (MIN) grabs and pulls Gobert's (UTA) right arm while reaching in for the steal.
Budinger (MIN) makes contact with Favors' (UTA) arm and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Wiggins (MIN) is in legal guarding position when Ingles (UTA) extends his right arm into him and clears space on the drive to the basket.
Favors (UTA) and Dieng (MIN) briefly engage while going for the entry pass.
L-Slash shows Dieng (MIN) makes contact with Favors' (UTA) face on the layup attempt.
Favors (UTA) his Dieng (MIN) on the arm/wrist, causing him to lose the ball.
Dieng (MIN) moves his pivot foot.
Favors (UTA) sets the screen on LaVine (MIN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Wiggins (MIN) was confirmed and Utah was awarded possession.
Budinger (MIN) maintains legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket by Favors (UTA).
LaVine (MIN) moves his pivot foot on the perimeter after the catch.
Millsap (UTA) cleanly strips the ball from LaVine (MIN).
Gobert (UTA) gets caught in the air defending the pump fake and lands on Dieng (MIN) as he attempts the jumpshot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the foul by Gobert (UTA) occurred before the shot clock expired was confirmed.
Budinger (MIN) handchecks Burke (UTA) and affects his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Kilpatrick (MIN).
Millsap (UTA) commits a take foul on LaVine (MIN).
